{"validation_override": true, "portal_release_date": "", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "", "catalog_type": "Data | Donn\u00e9es", "title_fra": "Soldats de la Premi\u00e8re Guerre mondiale - CEC", "keywords": "military, war, soldier, canada, expeditionary force, cef, first world war, wwi, 1914, 1918", "data_series_issue_identification": "001042", "ready_to_publish": "", "id": "6a6e6a79-9e2a-48cc-99ec-163da26d15e9", "subject": "Military  Histoire et science militaire", "data_series_name_fra": "", "spatial_representation_type": "", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Quarterly | Trimestriel", "title": "Soldiers of the First World War - CEF", "author_email": "open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Plus de 600 000 hommes et femmes se sont enr\u00f4l\u00e9s dans le Corps exp\u00e9ditionnaire canadien (CEC) pendant la Premi\u00e8re Guerre mondiale (1914-1918) en tant que soldats, infirmi\u00e8res et aum\u00f4niers. La base de donn\u00e9es est un index \u00e0 partir duquel il est possible de consulter leurs dossiers de service, lesquels sont conserv\u00e9s \u00e0 Biblioth\u00e8que et Archives Canada.", "digital_object_identifier": "", "presentation_form": "", "spatial": "", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "http://registry.data.gc.ca/commonwebsol/fileuploads/B/B/3/BB31EB47-4586-44BE-9D5D-C564C8CEF840/001042-txt-e.xml|001042-txt-e.xml", "language": "eng; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/databases/cef/001042-130-e.html", "language": "eng; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://registry.data.gc.ca/commonwebsol/fileuploads/2/D/2/2D283451-5640-45FB-8F78-9D3AF936CB59/001042-txt-f.xml|001042-txt-f.xml", "language": "fra; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/base-de-donnees/cec/001042-130-f.html", "language": "fra; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.collectionscan