{"validation_override": true, "portal_release_date": "", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "", "catalog_type": "Data | Donn\u00e9es", "title_fra": "Cartes et Plans du Canada", "keywords": "map, plan, chart, canada, history, cartography ", "data_series_issue_identification": "001028", "ready_to_publish": "", "id": "becd58f5-2751-4455-b3c2-21f5c3a923ae", "subject": "History and Archaeology  Histoire et arch\u00e9ologie", "data_series_name_fra": "", "spatial_representation_type": "", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Quarterly | Trimestriel", "title": "Maps, Plans and Charts of Canada", "author_email": "open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Depuis leur cr\u00e9ation en 1872, les Archives nationales du Canada, maintenant Biblioth\u00e8que et Archives Canada, acqui\u00e8rent, conservent et comm\u00e9morent le patrimoine cartographique du Canada. Aujourd'hui, ces fonds renferment plus de 2 millions de pi\u00e8ces. L'instrument de recherche suivant permet aux chercheurs de consulter environ 40 000 descriptions \u00e0 la pi\u00e8ce du \u00ab vieux catalogue sur fiches \u00bb. Ces documents sont d\u00e9crits dans la langue du cr\u00e9ateur; la plupart des descriptions n'existent qu'en anglais.", "digital_object_identifier": "", "presentation_form": "", "spatial": "", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/archivianet/02015401_e.html", "language": "eng; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/archivianet/02015401_f.html", "language": "fra; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/obj/900/f11/001028_20100929.xml", "language": "eng; CAN | fra; CAN", "resource_type": "file", "format": "XML"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "", "endpoint_url_fra": "", "date_published": "2004-03-31", "time_period_coverage_start": "1872-01-01", "data_series_name": "", "url_fra": "", "endpoint_url": "", "time_period_coverage_end": "1872-01-01", "language": "", "date_modified": "2010-08-05", "url": "", "notes": "Since its inception in 1872, the National Archives of Canada, now Library and Archives Canada, has acquired, preserved and commemorated the cartographic heritage of Canada and there are now some two million items in the collection. This search tool provides access to approximately 40,000 item-level descriptions from the \"old map card catalogue.\" The item-level descriptions are written in the language of the original map, plan, or chart; the majority of the descriptions are written in English.", "owner_org": "75BDAB68-199F-4C06-92A3-E1E6769B0B8E", "keywords_fra": "carte, plan, charte, canada, histoire, cartographie", "resource_type": "file"}
{"validation_override": true, "portal_release_date": "", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "", "catalog_type": "Data | Donn\u00e9es", "title_fra": "Fichiers m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques canadiens pour l'\u00e9nergie et le g\u00e9nie (FMCEG)", "keywords": "weather data ", "data_series_issue_identification": "", "ready_to_publish": "", "id": "79e894ce-bfce-4df5-a204-9195e5a4193e", "subject": "Nature and Environment  Nature et environnement", "data_series_name_fra": "", "spatial_representation_type": "", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Unknown | Inconnu", "title": "Canadian Weather Energy and Engineering Datasets (CWEEDS)", "author_email": "open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "\"Ensemble de donn\u00e9es informatis\u00e9es sur des conditions horaires de 21 \u00e9l\u00e9ments m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques pour un emplacement donn\u00e9. Les ensembles de donn\u00e9es peuvent remonter \u00e0 aussi loin que 1953 et se terminent pour la plupart en 2005. Les FMCEG comprennent les observations m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques \u00e0 long terme n\u00e9cessaires \u00e0 l'am\u00e9nagement urbain et \u00e0 la conception d'\u00e9difices \u00e9conerg\u00e9tiques. Ce qui importe encore davantage est que les FMCEG permettent d'estimer le rayonnement solaire horaire (au moyen d'un mod\u00e8le) pour les lieux d'observation m\u00e9t\u00e9orolopgique o\u00f9 le rayonnement solaire n'est pas relev\u00e9.\n\"\n", "digital_object_identifier": "", "presentation_form": "", "spatial": "", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "ftp://arcdm20.tor.ec.gc.ca/pub/dist/climate/CWEEDS_2005/ZIPPED%20FILES/ENGLISH/", "language": "eng; CAN | fra; CAN", "resource_type": "file", "format": "CSV"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "", "endpoint_url_fra": "", "date_published": "2010-04-22", "time_period_coverage_start": "1953-01-01", "data_series_name": "", "url_fra": "http://www.climate.weatheroffice.gc.ca/Welcome_f.html?&", "endpoint_url": "", "time_period_coverage_end": "1953-01-01", "language": "", "date_modified": "", "url": "http://www.climate.weatheroffice.gc.ca/Welcome_e.html", "notes": "\"A computer dataset of hourly conditions for 21 weather elements occurring at a specific location. Datasets may begin as early as 1953 and end for most in 2005. CWEEDS files include the long term weather records necessary for urban planning and the design of energy efficient buildings. Most importantly, CWEEDS files provide the provision of estimated hourly solar radiation amounts (through the use of a model), for weather observation locations at which solar radiation is not observed. \n\"\n", "owner_org": "49E2ADF4-AD7A-43EB-85C8-6433D37ED62C", "keywords_fra": "donn\u00e9es m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques", "resource_type": "file"}
{"validation_override": true, "portal_release_date": "", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "", "catalog_type": "Data | Donn\u00e9es", "title_fra": "Fichiers m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques canadiens pour calcul \u00e9nerg\u00e9tique (FMCCE)", "keywords": "temperature data ", "data_series_issue_identification": "", "ready_to_publish": "", "id": "d2fab74f-3c92-4f76-8676-c26a95f6c3a1", "subject": "Economics and Industry  \u00c9conomie et industrie", "data_series_name_fra": "", "spatial_representation_type": "", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Unknown | Inconnu", "title": "Canadian Weather Year for Energy Calculation (CWEC)", "author_email": "open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Ensembles de donn\u00e9es cr\u00e9\u00e9es en combinant 12 mois m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques types choisis \u00e0 partir d'une base de donn\u00e9es couvrant habituellement 30 ans de donn\u00e9es des FMCEG. Les mois sont choisis par une comparaison statistique des moyennes mensuelles individuelles et des moyennes mensuelles \u00e0 long terme au regard du rayonnement global quotidien total, des temp\u00e9ratures du thermom\u00e8tre sec moyennes, minimales et maximales, des temp\u00e9ratures du point de ros\u00e9e moyennes, minimales et maximales ainsi que des vitesses du vent moyennes et maximales.\n", "digital_object_identifier": "", "presentation_form": "", "spatial": "", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "ftp://arcdm20.tor.ec.gc.ca/pub/dist/climate/CWEC/ENGLISH/", "language": "eng; CAN | fra; CAN", "resource_type": "file", "format": "CSV"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "", "endpoint_url_fra": "", "date_published": "2010-04-22", "time_period_coverage_start": "1953-01-01", "data_series_name": "", "url_fra": "http://www.climate.weatheroffice.gc.ca/Welcome_f.html?&", "endpoint_url": "", "time_period_coverage_end": "1953-01-01", "language": "", "date_modified": "", "url": "http://www.climate.weatheroffice.gc.ca/Welcome_e.html", "notes": "Datasets created by joining twelve Typical Meteorological Months selected from a database of, usually, 30 years of CWEEDS data. The months are chosen by statistically comparing individual monthly means with long term monthly means for daily total global radiation, mean, minimum and maximum dry bulb temperature, mean, minimum and maximum dew point temperature, and mean and maximum wind speed.\n", "owner_org": "49E2ADF4-AD7A-43EB-85C8-6433D37ED62C", "keywords_fra": "donn\u00e9es de temp\u00e9rature", "resource_type": "file"}
{"validation_override": true, "portal_release_date": "", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "", "catalog_type": "Data | Donn\u00e9es", "title_fra": "Ensemble de donn\u00e9es t\u00e9l\u00e9chargeables de l'Inventaire national des rejets de polluants (INRP) - 1985 - 2008", "keywords": "pollutant, pollution, emissions, environment, recycling, disposal, industry, chemical substances", "data_series_issue_identification": "", "ready_to_publish": "", "id": "005701dc-7acb-4258-8176-ad0eb8dcc5b0", "subject": "Nature and Environment  Nature et environnement", "data_series_name_fra": "Ensembles de donn\u00e9es de l'Inventaire national des rejets de polluants (INRP)", "spatial_representation_type": "", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Unknown | Inconnu", "title": "National Pollutant Release Inventory (NPRI) Downloadable Datasets - 1985 - 2008", "author_email": "open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "L'Inventaire national des rejets de polluants (INRP) est l'inventaire public du Canada sur les polluants rejet\u00e9s (dans l'atmosph\u00e8re, dans l'eau et dans le sol), \u00e9limin\u00e9s et recycl\u00e9s. L'INRP comprend: (1) Des donn\u00e9es et des renseignements au sujet des polluants rejet\u00e9s (dans l'atmosph\u00e8re, dans l'eau et dans le sol), \u00e9limin\u00e9s et recycl\u00e9s qui sont d\u00e9clar\u00e9s par les installations (plus de 8000 installations) et publi\u00e9s par le Gouvernement du Canada en vertu de la Loi canadienne sur la protection de l'environnement, 1999 [LCPE (1999)].  (2) Des sommaires complets et des tendances li\u00e9s aux \u00e9missions des principaux polluants atmosph\u00e9riques. Ceux-ci s'appuient sur des donn\u00e9es d\u00e9clar\u00e9es par les installations ainsi que sur les \u00e9missions provenant d'autres sources telles que les v\u00e9hicules \u00e0 moteurs, le chauffage r\u00e9sidentiel, les feux de for\u00eat et l'agriculture.  Ces polluants comprennent les principaux contaminants atmosph\u00e9riques (principaux polluants contribuant au smog, \u00e0 la formation de pluies acides et/ou \u00e0 la pi\u00e8tre qualit\u00e9 de l'air), les m\u00e9taux lourds s\u00e9lectionn\u00e9s et les polluants organiques persistants.  Il y  a plusieurs facteurs \u00e0 consid\u00e9rer lors de l'analyse des donn\u00e9es de l'INRP et d'autres renseignements, sont disponibles au site web de l'INRP.  Les donn\u00e9es de l'INRP sont disponibles dans plusieurs formats : un outils de recherche; des bases de donn\u00e9es, des feuilles de calcul ainsi que des couches cartographiques Google EarthMC t\u00e9l\u00e9chargeables.", "digital_object_identifier": "", "presentation_form": "", "spatial": "", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/inrp-npri/default.asp?lang=en&n=0EC58C98-", "language": "eng; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/inrp-npri/default.asp?lang=En&n=B5C1EAB8-1", "language": "eng; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/inrp-npri/default.asp?lang=Fr&n=0EC58C98-", "language": "fra; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}, {"url": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/inrp-npri/default.asp?lang=Fr&n=42083AB9-1", "language": "fra; CAN", "resource_type": "doc", "format": "HTML"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "", "endpoint_url_fra": "", "date_published": "2010-01-01", "time_period_coverage_start": "1985-01-01", "data_series_name": "National Pollutant Release Inventory (NPRI) Datasets", "url_fra": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/inrp-npri/", "endpoint_url": "", "time_period_coverage_end": "1985-01-01", "language": "", "date_modified": "", "url": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/inrp-npri/", "notes": "The National Pollutant Release Inventory (NPRI) is Canada's public inventory of pollutant releases (to air, water and land), disposals and transfers for recycling. The NPRI includes:  (1) Data and information on pollutant releases, disposals and transfers for recycling that is reported by facilities (more than 8000) and published by Environment Canada under the authority Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999 (CEPA 1999).  (2) Comprehensive emission summaries and trends for key air pollutants, based on facility-reported data and emission estimates for other sources such as motor vehicles, residential heating, forest fires and agriculture.  These pollutants include criteria air contaminants (the main pollutants contributing to smog, acid rain and/or poor air quality), several heavy metals and persistent organic pollutants.   There are a number of important factors that should be considered prior to the use and interpretation of NPRI data and additional information is available on the NPRI web site.  NPRI data is available in a number of formats:  online query tools, downloadable databases and spreadsheets as well as map layers. ", "owner_org": "49E2ADF4-AD7A-43EB-85C8-6433D37ED62C", "keywords_fra": "pollutant, pollution, emissions, environnement, recyclage, elimination, industrie, substances chimiques", "resource_type": "file"}
